snippet.title: Medal of Honor E3 Multiplayer Trailer [HD]
snippet.description: Partnering with DICE, Medal of Honor will deliver an exciting and adrenaline-filled multiplayer experience. From the makers of the Battlefield franchise, Medal of Honor multiplayer goes back to basics with heart-pounding gameplay, played in close quarters where individual player skill is the most important tool for survival.
